verdict.recommendation:
Check the return value of send() and only set isCashed to true if the send succeeded. Better yet, use the withdrawal pattern: store the winner's pending balance and let them withdraw it themselves. Example fix:

```solidity
bool sent = winner.send(subpot);
if (sent) {
    rounds[roundIndex].isCashed[subpotIndex] = true;
}
```

Or preferably, use a pull payment pattern:
```solidity
pendingWithdrawals[winner] += subpot;
rounds[roundIndex].isCashed[subpotIndex] = true;
```
with a separate withdraw() function.
